<p>Relaxation: The sizzling sensation clambered onto the back of one horse for a ride and at another point she lay on the grass as another horse ambled about nearby</p>

<p>She could be glimpsed through the window wearing an old-fashioned bomber jacket and a pair of khakis and petting the animal.</p>

<p>Her horse posts come hours after she set the Internet ablaze with a throwback snap taken on the farm this June with Gigi.</p>

<p>Gigi is expecting her firstborn child with her boyfriend Zayn Malik and could be seen in the snap cradling her baby bump in a dress. </p>

